This article is about the theological viewpoint. For the socio-political movement see [[Universal opportunity]].

[[Universal opportunity]] is the idea, particularly in [[Christianity]], that an opportunity to follow the deity, e.g. [[Jesus]], will be an option at the time of death.[http://www.religioustolerance.org/chr_savn.htm]

